item.title: CVE-2024-23941|2024-02-01T03:56:12.231Z -- Intermesh BV -- Group Office
item.description: Cross-site scripting vulnerability exists in Group Office prior to v6.6.182, prior to v6.7.64 and prior to v6.8.31, which may allow a remote authenticated attacker to execute an arbitrary script on the web browser of the user who is logging in to the product.
